<li>Your dad will be deeply missed. He was such a kind and loving person.</li>
<li>May your beautiful memories bring you comfort during this sad time.</li>
<li>He was a wonderful father, and his memory will live on in your hearts.</li>
<li>I can't imagine the pain you must be feeling.  Please know I'm here for you.</li>
<li>Words cannot express how sorry I am for your loss.  Praying for your family.</li>
<li>Holding you and your family close in my heart and thoughts.</li>
<li>Your dad's legacy of love will continue through you.</li>
<li>May his memory be a blessing to you and your family.</li>
<li>I'm deeply saddened by the loss of your father. He will be greatly missed.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and peace as you grieve the loss of your father.</li>
<li>Cherish the precious memories you have of your dad.</li>
<li>With heartfelt sympathy, I offer my deepest condolences.</li>
    

